dc_description_s: Ambridge and Economy, Beaver County, Pennsylvania, Oct. 1905. 1 map on 10 sheets : col. ; sheets 65 x 54 cm. Statement of responsibility: Sanborn Map Company.  Cadastral map.  Title from sheet 1.  Oriented with north to the upper right on some sheets.  October 1905.""  Sheet 7, for ""French Point,"" is at a scale of 1:1,200.  Includes sheet index map, street and ""Specials"" indexes, key, notes, and text."". Scale approximately 1:600. 50 ft. to an in. unless otherwise noted on individual sheets.
